title: Uptown--3 blocks to the Lakes--NEW RENOVATION
posting_body: ['Beautiful 1 bedroom unit has new renovated open kitchen with granite counter-tops and stainless steel appliances including dishwasher as well as a renovated bath, wood floors, lots of light, just a couple of blocks to the chain of lakes.', "You can't beat the location of the wonderful brick building at 3332 Hennepin Avenue within walking distance of the lakes and all of Uptown's amazing restaurants, coffee shops, nightlife, boutiques, national stores, salons, grocery stores, and movie theatres.", 'Walk, bike, kayak at the lakes just a couple of blocks away.', 'Work out at CorePower Yoga, Lifetime Fitness, and the YWCA.', 'Minutes to downtown with easy access to bike on the Greenway or take the bus.', 'Includes heat, water and trash.', 'On-site laundry and storage, off-street parking available and cats are permitted.', 'Call Jim at', 'show contact info', 'to set up your appointment today!', 'Available October 1.']
